title: Competition Reloading with Brian Enos
description:
I thank BobTheBuilder2 for uploading this here....I am simply transferring a few torrents here so they get more popularity, and to add it to my 'curriculum.' ;)

"Brian Enos guides you through a complete step-by-step reloading process for IPSC, Steel Challenge and NRA/Bianchi Cup style shooting. Using a Dillon 650 press to demonstrate proper reloading techniques for the most popular loads used by top shooters, he answers questions and explains techniques not found in loading manuals. Reveals information you may never see or hear anywhere else.   Also includes an excellent tips section, and shooting video footage."
